%YAML 1.1
%TAG !u! tag:unity3d.com,2011:
--- !u!114 &11400000
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 9e7c527a6f66a8c49a6fab10a94681fc, type: 3}
  m_Name: Day3MorningN
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  sequenceId: albert_day3_morning_nopill
  lines:
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Morning, Andy. Another beautiful day aboard the SUNSET16. DOLOS assigned
      you a task at the boiler room. A fuse broke late last night there, and needs
      some maintenance. You know the drill. Do your task and keep DOLOS happy.
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Sounds good to me.
      nextLineIndex: 1
      offPillChoice: 0
    - choiceText: Another day, another wire.
      nextLineIndex: 2
      offPillChoice: 0
    - choiceText: A fuse blew last night? What caused it?
      nextLineIndex: 13
      offPillChoice: 1
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That\u2019s the spirit. Just keep on with those designated tasks."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "How it usually is. It\u2019s good you\u2019re like that."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Any questions before you head out? My shift starts soon, but I have some
      time to burn.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices:
    - choiceText: Any word on when more passengers are supposed to arrive? The ship
        feels empty sometimes.
      nextLineIndex: 4
      offPillChoice: 0
    - choiceText: "How\u2019s the nuclear core these days?"
      nextLineIndex: 5
      offPillChoice: 0
    - choiceText: Heard anything about that NUSA CEO? After the bankruptcy scandal?
      nextLineIndex: 8
      offPillChoice: 0
    - choiceText: I found something weird in the system yesterday. Old technician
        log. The name was Fiske. Mean anything to you?
      nextLineIndex: 14
      offPillChoice: 1
    advanceToLine: 11
    repeat: 1
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Last I checked, passenger rotations were delayed indefinitely. Corporate
      restructuring, I think. However, that was a few months ago. There\u2019s no
      need to pay it any mind now."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Smooth sailing as usual. The graphs are flat, and the readings are stable.
      Boring, but that\u2019s the goal. There was a time when the core was\u2026
      malfunctioning."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Really? How so?
      nextLineIndex: 6
      offPillChoice: 0
    - choiceText: "Nothing you can\u2019t handle."
      nextLineIndex: 7
      offPillChoice: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "The cooling system was starting to fail. Worked my magic and turned things
      around. That\u2019s why they hired me."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "That\u2019s for certain. It\u2019s part of the job package."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Last I heard, she had connections in China. After that, I don\u2019t know
      much. The rest of the shareholders scattered to other conglomerates in North
      America and Europe."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 9
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Why\u2019d you ask?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: Could the same happen here?
      nextLineIndex: 10
      offPillChoice: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "DOLOS is different. More structured than other mega corporations. We\u2019re
      not going anywhere. And neither are you."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: 
    sendDelay: 0
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: I have no more questions.
      nextLineIndex: 12
      offPillChoice: 0
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Alright, I\u2019ll catch you later then."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: -1
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: The initial DOLOS report cited a minor power fluctuation. Probably some
      wear and tear. Nothing too serious.
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 1
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.5
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026That\u2019s a name I haven\u2019t seen in a while. Where\u2019d
      you find those?"
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 0
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: A terminal in C-12, behind a panel.
      nextLineIndex: 15
      offPillChoice: 1
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Pay no attention to them. Files like that are old and are sometimes corrupted
      with malware. You\u2019ll get your tablet infected if you keep interacting
      with it. DOLOS issued an announcement a while ago on matters like this. You
      should brush up on it."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 2
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0
    choices:
    - choiceText: "Then\u2026 who was Fiske?"
      nextLineIndex: 16
      offPillChoice: 1
    advanceToLine: 0
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
  - speakerName: Albert
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "\u2026Someone who didn\u2019t follow protocol. He was put on administrative
      leave for an undisclosed amount of time. We shouldn\u2019t talk about him anymore.
      Listen to DOLOS and adhere to your contract, as you have been doing these past
      5 years."
    sendDelay: 1
    delayRepeats: 2
    autoAdvanceDelay: 0.01
    choices: []
    advanceToLine: 3
    repeat: 0
    repeated: 0
